cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.AI. 

The paper focuses on optimizing the convergence time of federated learning over wireless networks, which involves joint learning, wireless resource allocation, and user selection. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.IT (Information Theory), as the paper deals with wireless network resource allocation and transmission. The paper also involves optimization and control, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
